data.description: Nestled in the serene landscape of Apple Valley, Utah, enveloped by stunning red mountains and natural vistas, this 1.27-acre property boasts a 2,856 sq ft, 3-bed, 3-bath home built in 2018, Alongside is a 1,128 sq ft 3-bed, 2-bath manufactured home, offering versatile living options. Notable features include a 1000-gallon water tank, hot tub pad, fenced areas for animals/agricultural use, and a convenient metal enclosed workshop. Endless possibilities for customization and potential rental income. Embrace rural tranquility with modern comforts. Schedule a tour to explore this exceptional property today!
